    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="交换机和终端设备的基本配置"><a href="#交换机和终端设备的基本配置" class="headerlink" title="交换机和终端设备的基本配置"></a>交换机和终端设备的基本配置</h2><p><strong>主机名配置</strong></p><p>1.配置主机名</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">Switch<span class="hljs-selector-id">#configure</span> terminal <br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#hostname</span> S1<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">S1</span><span class="hljs-params">(config)</span></span>#<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.恢复默认主机名</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">S1<span class="hljs-selector-id">#configure</span> terminal <br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">S1</span><span class="hljs-params">(config)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#no</span> hostname <br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config)</span></span>#<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>密码配置</strong></p><p>1.设置控制台密码（配置用户模式密码，使用<strong>login</strong>命令启用用户访问）</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">Switch<span class="hljs-selector-id">#configure</span> terminal <br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#line</span> console <span class="hljs-number">0</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config-line)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#password</span> cisco<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config-line)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#login</span> <br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config-line)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#end</span><br>Switch#<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.取消控制台密码</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">Switch<span class="hljs-selector-id">#configure</span> terminal <br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#line</span> console <span class="hljs-number">0</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config-line)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#no</span> password <br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#end</span><br>Switch#<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3.设置特权模式密码</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">Switch<span class="hljs-selector-id">#configure</span> terminal <br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#enable</span> secret cisco<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#exit</span><br>Switch#<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>4.取消特权模式密码</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">Switch<span class="hljs-selector-id">#configure</span> terminal <br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#no</span> enable secret <br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#exit</span><br>Switch#<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>5.设置远程访问密码</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">Switch<span class="hljs-selector-id">#configure</span> terminal<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#line</span> vty <span class="hljs-number">0</span> <span class="hljs-number">15</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config-line)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#password</span> cisco<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config-line)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#login</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config-line)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#end</span><br>Switch#<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>6.取消远程访问密码</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">Switch<span class="hljs-selector-id">#configure</span> terminal <br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#line</span> vty <span class="hljs-number">0</span> <span class="hljs-number">15</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config-line)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#no</span> password <br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config-line)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#end</span><br>Switch#<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>7.密码加密</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">Switch<span class="hljs-selector-id">#configure</span> terminal <br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#service</span> password-encryption <br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config)</span></span>#<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>8.验证密码是否加密</p><figure class="highlight pgsql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs pgsql">Switch#<span class="hljs-keyword">show</span> running-config<br>!<br>!<br><span class="hljs-type">line</span> con <span class="hljs-number">0</span><br> <span class="hljs-keyword">login</span><br>!<br><span class="hljs-type">line</span> vty <span class="hljs-number">0</span> <span class="hljs-number">4</span><br> <span class="hljs-keyword">password</span> <span class="hljs-number">7</span> <span class="hljs-number">0822455</span>D0A16<br> <span class="hljs-keyword">login</span><br><span class="hljs-type">line</span> vty <span class="hljs-number">5</span> <span class="hljs-number">15</span><br> <span class="hljs-keyword">password</span> <span class="hljs-number">7</span> <span class="hljs-number">0822455</span>D0A16<br> <span class="hljs-keyword">login</span><br>!<br>!<br>!<br><span class="hljs-keyword">end</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>旗标消息</strong></p><p>1.配置旗标消息</p><figure class="highlight autoit"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs autoit"><span class="hljs-keyword">Switch</span><span class="hljs-meta">#configure terminal </span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">Switch</span>(config)<span class="hljs-meta">#banner motd #Authorized Access Only#</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">Switch</span>(config)<span class="hljs-meta">#</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>保存配置</strong></p><p><strong>startup-config（启动配置文件 NVRAM）</strong><br><strong>running-config（运行配置文件 RAM）</strong></p><p>1.查看存储在RAM中的配置</p><figure class="highlight autoit"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs autoit"><span class="hljs-keyword">Switch</span><span class="hljs-meta">#show running-config </span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.查看启动配置文件</p><figure class="highlight autoit"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs autoit"><span class="hljs-keyword">Switch</span><span class="hljs-meta">#show startup-config </span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>3.把运行配置保存到启动文件</strong></p><figure class="highlight lua"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs lua">Switch#copy <span class="hljs-built_in">running</span>-<span class="hljs-built_in">config</span> startup-<span class="hljs-built_in">config</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>修改运行配置</strong></p><p>1.重新加载设配（删除未保存的运行配置，运行启动配置文件）</p><p>重新加载时，IOS会检测到发生改变的运行配置文件没有保存到启动配置文件，因此，它将显示一则消息，询问是否保存更改。</p><figure class="highlight autoit"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs autoit"><span class="hljs-keyword">Switch</span><span class="hljs-meta">#reload </span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.清除启动配置</p><figure class="highlight autoit"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs autoit"><span class="hljs-keyword">Switch</span><span class="hljs-meta">#erase startup-config </span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>交换机虚拟接口配置</strong></p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">Switch<span class="hljs-selector-id">#configure</span> terminal <br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#interface</span> vlan <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config-if)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#ip</span> <span class="hljs-selector-tag">address</span> <span class="hljs-number">192.168</span>.<span class="hljs-number">1.20</span> <span class="hljs-number">255.255</span>.<span class="hljs-number">255.0</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config-if)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#ip</span> default-gateway <span class="hljs-number">192.168</span>.<span class="hljs-number">1.1</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-title">Switch</span><span class="hljs-params">(config-if)</span></span><span class="hljs-selector-id">#no</span> shutdown <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
